{
  "id": "alerting-notifications-create-mute-timing",
  "title": "Create time intervals for common scenarios",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "Time intervals define the recurring windows when notifications should be suppressed. You'll create two time intervals: one for a weekly maintenance window and one for non-business hours."
    },
    {
      "type": "multistep",
      "content": "Navigate to **Alerts & IRM > Alerting > Notification configuration**.",
      "requirements": ["navmenu-open"],
      "steps": [
        { "action": "highlight", "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/alerts-and-incidents']" },
        { "action": "highlight", "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/alerting']" },
        { "action": "highlight", "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/alerting/notifications']" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive",
      "action": "highlight",
      "reftarget": "[data-testid='data-testid Tab Time intervals']",
      "content": "Click the **Time intervals** tab.",
      "requirements": ["on-page:/alerting/notifications"]
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "Create maintenance window time interval",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[href*='mute-timing/new']",
          "content": "Click **+ Add time interval**."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='mute-timing-name']",
          "targetvalue": "Sunday maintenance window",
          "content": "In the **Name** field, enter `Sunday maintenance window`."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='mute-timing-starts-at']",
          "targetvalue": "02:00",
          "content": "In the **Start time** field, enter `02:00`."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='mute-timing-ends-at']",
          "targetvalue": "04:00",
          "content": "In the **End time** field, enter `04:00`."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Sun",
          "content": "In the **Days of the week** field, select **Sunday**."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "Leave the **Location** blank or select your preferred timezone."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Save time interval",
          "content": "Click **Save time interval** to create the time interval."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "The time interval appears in the Time intervals list."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "Create non-business hours time interval",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "a[href*='mute-timing/new']",
          "content": "On the **Time intervals** tab, click **+ Add time interval**."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='mute-timing-name']",
          "targetvalue": "Non-business hours",
          "content": "In the **Name** field, enter `Non-business hours`."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='mute-timing-starts-at']",
          "targetvalue": "18:00",
          "content": "In the **Start time** field, enter `18:00`."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='mute-timing-ends-at']",
          "targetvalue": "23:59",
          "content": "In the **End time** field, enter `23:59`."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Add another time range",
          "content": "Click **+ Add another time range** to cover the early morning hours."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "In the second time range, enter Start time `00:00` and End time `08:00`. This covers the full overnight window from 6 PM to 8 AM."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "In the **Days of the week** field, select **Monday** through **Friday**. Leave the **Location** blank or select your preferred timezone."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Add another time interval item",
          "content": "Click **Add another time interval item** to add weekend coverage."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "For the weekend interval, leave **Start time** and **End time** blank to match all times."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Sat",
          "content": "In the **Days of the week** field, select **Saturday**."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Sun",
          "content": "Select **Sunday**."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Save time interval",
          "content": "Click **Save time interval** to create the time interval."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "The time interval now covers weekday nights (6 PM to 8 AM) and all day on weekends."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
